history.content:
Cal Central has automatically added eligible students to the Sp 17 degree list, please check your "Notifications", and you should find the following message in "My Dashboard"

You should also see it listed under "Terms Information" in "My Academics" under your picture as follows: 

If you were added to the degree list, but don't want to graduate in sp 17, please follow the listed instructions in the message or check "Opting Out.." section of this webpage.

If you want to graduate in sp 17 and were not automatically added, please fill out an Add to degree form and turn it into 2nd floor of Evans Hall. The deadline is March 10, 2017
